{"tid":1577530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屍體不是高秀蘭（集體討論）","createTime":"2019-09-17T17:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T05:26:09.000Z","uid":297248,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5f89bc39d334b5dde79f6d886fd3ac96032d317f","tid":1577530,"uid":297248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"1 屍體頭部只淨骨頭,屍身變乾屍, 代表屍體必定被處理過,目的是要隱瞞屍體身份。<br />\n2 如果屍體被處理，但衣服完好。代表處理過程是先脫屍體衣服，處理屍體後才為屍體穿著衣服。<br />\n3 如果屍體已被處理得體無完膚，經已不能辨別屍體身份，又何必多此一舉為屍體穿衣？<br />\n<br />\n結論：有人刻意引導公眾屍體身份是高秀蘭，屍體有可能另有其人。"},{"pid":"167a06b258637cb42a5063242096f3d553ab2d4e","tid":1577530,"uid":249846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ddb03c717ef503e5e09fc383d5f988f2b405f7","tid":1577530,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過，依家個人越諗越驚，情緒有d混亂"},{"pid":"e5cb04831ced201bf82a7d89e7709e72eece2151","tid":1577530,"uid":297248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3ddb03c717ef503e5e09fc383d5f988f2b405f7","tid":1577530,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過，依家個人越諗越驚，情緒有d混亂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"我都係，好心寒。"},{"pid":"4938c7b561792d3789258dac3828c7a507cb0152","tid":1577530,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"驗唔到DNA？骨頭呀頭髮之類"},{"pid":"f4be71f7532e33a3a3a3ac70c03ff6552ead5917","tid":1577530,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"唔係高秀蘭唔通係有人cap圖係太子站果個女人<br />\n果個女人又唔太似高秀蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f41658518e8e4d5632f0b9ec5e3c5c6269b570","tid":1577530,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:53:57.000Z","msg":"我都相信你嘅講法，反正政府的說話就不相信了"},{"pid":"5d5410d64587ab8ce45a119a26ea8fee3359b7bb","tid":1577530,"uid"